STATEMIXIN
==========
refreshData()
see bank-form
- refreshData is a prop 
- use refreshData() as expected

where its being called - 
refreshData = {() => this.fetchData(provider.id)}
becomes => 
refreshData = {() => fetchData(provider.id)}

-or-
refreshData = {() this.fetchData()}
becomes => 
refreshData = {() => refreshData()}
and 
const refreshData = () => {
  setShowForm(false);
  fetchData();
}

